  • Classes in org.glassfish.admin.amx.config used by org.glassfish.admin.amx.base 
    Class and Description
    AMXConfigProxy
    Deprecated. 
    Extending this proxy interface implies that the class is part of the MBean API for configuration, that the interface is a dynamic proxy to a config MBean.

    Note that considerable metadata is available for config MBeans, via MBeanInfo.getDescriptor().

    AttributeResolver
    Deprecated. 
    Interface implemented by MBeans which can resolve a variable to a value. Variable attributes are strings of the form ${...} and are returned as the values of certain Attributes. This interface is intended for use only with config MBeans.
